I actually used to like this spot alot. I used to come here almost every day but the last couple of times I went the staff haven't been the best to me. When I last went the guy seemed in a bad mood and he was making a sandwich for a online order which was fine but when he was making my sandwich he stopped to get started on two sandwiches for a online order. At first was like uh ok whatever it's late at night (1-2am) but after my sandwich was toasted and done he ignored it and kept making the two sandwiches for the people who weren't even in the store. He should have finished my sandwich first and then made the two sandwiches. Then he gets angry when I asked him to use spinach from the fuller side because the other side you could tell that he hasn't refilled anything for hours. The guy was rude.  I won't be going back.
